    dc:description "FIGURES 8–11. Paralleloalathrips bivenatus gen. et sp. n. (8) holotype female, dorsal view, fore wings indicated; (9) paratype female, indicated: fungal spores; (10) holotype female, left fore wing; (11) paratype male, basal abdominal tergites, indicated: dorsolateral grooves on tergum II (met: metanotum, pt: pelta, mpII: medial plate of tergum II, lpII: lateral plate of tergum II, III: tergum III)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6796613/files/figure.png" ;
